    <hr>
    <p>The IBMM Prize was established in 2006 and is awarded biennially at IBMM conference to an early career ion beam researcher (up to 7 years since obtaining the Ph.D degree) who has made an outstanding contribution to the field. Nominations should include at least one recommendation letter, and a CV with a list of publications. Self-nomination is also acceptable. Please send the nomination package to Prof. Rob Elliman (rob.elliman@anu.edu.au). The closing date is May 1, 2018.</p>

